                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "This character insists on hauling every trinket they own\u2014pots, cloaks, a lucky rock\u2014until they\u2019re a walking junk pile. Their back bends under the load, and they stagger where others stride. They refuse to lighten up, claiming it\u2019s all essential. Their strength sags under their own stubbornness.",
